{
  "uid": "api-overview",
  "title": "Application API Overview - RED Method",
  "description": "Primary RED method dashboard for the Application NestJS backend. Monitors Rate, Errors, and Duration using Tempo span metrics and OTLP application metrics.",
  "tags": ["app-backend", "nestjs", "api", "red-method"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": ["5s", "10s", "30s", "1m", "5m"],
    "time_options": ["5m", "15m", "1h", "6h", "12h", "24h", "7d"]
  },
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "liveNow": false,
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "links": [],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {
          "selected": false,
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prometheus"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "queryValue": "",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "current": {},
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "${datasource}"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total, service)",
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "name": "service",
        "options": [],
        "query": {
          "qryType": 1,
          "query": "label_values(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total, service)",
          "refId": "PrometheusVariableQueryEditor-VariableQuery"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "sort": 1,
        "type": "query",
        "allValue": ".*"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 50,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "# Application API - RED Method Dashboard\n\nMonitors the **Rate** (request throughput), **Errors** (failure ratio), and **Duration** (latency distribution) for the Application NestJS backend.\n\n**Metric sources:** Tempo span metrics (`traces_spanmetrics_*`) and OTLP application metrics (`http_server_request_duration_seconds_*`). Queries use `or` fallbacks to display whichever source is available."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Overview Stats",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Total Request Rate",
      "description": "Total HTTP requests per second across all endpoints.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])) or sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "req/s",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true,
        "showPercentChange": true,
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 14,
          "valueSize": 36
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Error Rate %",
      "description": "Percentage of requests returning 5xx status codes. Red when above 5%.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "100 * (\n  (\n    sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\", status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m]))\n    or sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m]))\n    or vector(0)\n  )\n  /\n  clamp_min(\n    sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m]))\n    or sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"}[5m]))\n    or vector(1)\n  , 1)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "error %",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "percent",
          "decimals": 2,
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true,
        "showPercentChange": true,
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 14,
          "valueSize": 36
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "P95 Latency",
      "description": "95th percentile request duration. Yellow above 1s, red above 2s.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95,\n  sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])) by (le)\n) / 1000\nor\nhistogram_quantile(0.95,\n  sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])) by (le)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "P95",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 2 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true,
        "showPercentChange": true,
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 14,
          "valueSize": 36
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Active Services",
      "description": "Number of distinct services currently reporting metrics.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "count(count by (service) (traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"})) or count(count by (service) (http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"})) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "services",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "none",
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true,
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 14,
          "valueSize": 36
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "id": 101,
      "title": "Traffic",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "Request Rate by Endpoint",
      "description": "HTTP requests per second grouped by endpoint (span_name or http.route).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "Tempo",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (span_name) (\n  rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])\n)",
          "legendFormat": "{{ span_name }}",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "OTLP",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (http_route) (\n  rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])\n)",
          "legendFormat": "{{ http_route }}",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true,
          "hide": false
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "req/s",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "title": "Status Code Distribution",
      "description": "Proportion of HTTP response status code classes (2xx, 4xx, 5xx).",
      "type": "piechart",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "2xx",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\", \"http.status_code\"=~\"2..\"}[5m])) or sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\", http_response_status_code=~\"2..\"}[5m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "2xx",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "4xx",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\", \"http.status_code\"=~\"4..\"}[5m])) or sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\", http_response_status_code=~\"4..\"}[5m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "4xx",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "5xx",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\", \"http.status_code\"=~\"5..\"}[5m])) or sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            }
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "2xx" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "4xx" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "yellow" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "5xx" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "pieType": "donut",
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "showLegend": true,
          "values": ["value", "percent"]
        },
        "displayLabels": ["percent"]
      }
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 17 },
      "id": 102,
      "title": "Latency",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "title": "Latency Percentiles P50 / P95 / P99",
      "description": "Request duration percentiles across all routes. Tempo span metrics are in milliseconds (divided by 1000), OTLP metrics are in seconds.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "P50",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50,\n  sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])) by (le)\n) / 1000\nor\nhistogram_quantile(0.50,\n  sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])) by (le)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "P50",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "P95",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95,\n  sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])) by (le)\n) / 1000\nor\nhistogram_quantile(0.95,\n  sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])) by (le)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "P95",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "P99",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99,\n  sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])) by (le)\n) / 1000\nor\nhistogram_quantile(0.99,\n  sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])) by (le)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "P99",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "duration",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "line+area" }
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 2 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "P50" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "P95" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "yellow" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "P99" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "title": "Request Duration Distribution",
      "description": "Heatmap of request duration buckets over time. Darker colors indicate higher request concentration.",
      "type": "heatmap",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(increase(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])) by (le)",
          "legendFormat": "{{ le }}",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true,
          "format": "heatmap"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(increase(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])) by (le)",
          "legendFormat": "{{ le }}",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true,
          "format": "heatmap",
          "hide": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "type": "log",
              "log": 2
            },
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "calculate": false,
        "cellGap": 1,
        "color": {
          "exponent": 0.5,
          "fill": "dark-orange",
          "mode": "scheme",
          "reverse": false,
          "scale": "exponential",
          "scheme": "Spectral",
          "steps": 128
        },
        "exemplars": {
          "color": "rgba(255,0,255,0.7)"
        },
        "filterValues": {
          "le": 1e-9
        },
        "legend": {
          "show": true
        },
        "rowsFrame": {
          "layout": "auto"
        },
        "showValue": "never",
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "yHistogram": true
        },
        "yAxis": {
          "axisLabel": "duration",
          "axisPlacement": "left",
          "reverse": false,
          "unit": "ms",
          "decimals": 0
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 26 },
      "id": 103,
      "title": "Errors & Slow Endpoints",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "title": "Error Rate Over Time",
      "description": "5xx error rate as a percentage of total requests over time. Red threshold line at 5%.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 27 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "TempoErrors",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "100 * (\n  sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\", status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m]))\n  /\n  clamp_min(sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])), 1)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "Error Rate (span metrics)",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "OTLPErrors",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "100 * (\n  sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m]))\n  /\n  clamp_min(sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])), 1)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "Error Rate (OTLP)",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "%",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "gradientMode": "scheme",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "line+area" }
          },
          "unit": "percent",
          "decimals": 2,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Error Rate (span metrics)" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Error Rate (OTLP)" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "title": "Top 10 Slowest Endpoints",
      "description": "Average request latency, P95, and request rate per endpoint, sorted by average duration descending.",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 27 },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "avg_latency",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "topk(10,\n  (\n    sum by (span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_sum{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m]))\n    /\n    clamp_min(sum by (span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m])), 0.001)\n  ) / 1000\n)\nor\ntopk(10,\n  sum by (http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_sum{service=~\"$service\"}[5m]))\n  /\n  clamp_min(sum by (http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"}[5m])), 0.001)\n)",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table"
        },
        {
          "refId": "p95_latency",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "topk(10,\n  histogram_quantile(0.95,\n    sum by (le, span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m]))\n  ) / 1000\n)\nor\ntopk(10,\n  histogram_quantile(0.95,\n    sum by (le, http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[5m]))\n  )\n)",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table"
        },
        {
          "refId": "req_rate",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "topk(10,\n  sum by (span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{service=~\"$service\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[5m]))\n)\nor\ntopk(10,\n  sum by (http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service=~\"$service\"}[5m]))\n)",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": { "type": "auto" },
            "inspect": false,
            "filterable": true
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "span_name" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "Endpoint" },
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 280 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "http_route" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "Endpoint" },
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 280 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Value #avg_latency" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "Avg Latency" },
              { "id": "unit", "value": "s" },
              { "id": "decimals", "value": 3 },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    { "color": "green", "value": null },
